value.0: A staple in the diets of many drow and duergar communities, these herd animals of the Underdark are small but powerfully built.

((The following is written in Drow))

By order of the Noble Council this caravan trail has been marked by Feirie Fire. Wander at your preil.

Dos ph'nin leaving protection d'nindol outpost. Sarn d'trolls au iaurrhen.

You are now leaving the protection of this outpost. Beware of trolls near and around the bridges.

House Shobalar mining outpost is located ahead. Off limits unless prior request has been granted. Employees have been ordered to attack on sight.
The stout planks of this bench have been worn smooth by years of use.

((The following is written in Dwarvish runes))

Here lay all that is left of the Dwarven court of Deep Helm. 

WIth spade and shovel we Delved deeper than our our forefathers cautioned. Driven by our lust for the ore we filled our vaults with Mithril and our hearts with bitternes until we awoke that which was not meant to be known.  Forever more this place shall be called Deep Folly. abandoned, watched, begrudged. 

An oath to every clan bestowed by birthright, to watch over this place. May the evel entombed never again be loosed.
